title: Wake on Lan

creator: Patrick Wuring
descriptionHtml:
Start your computer with this simple app!

Features:

* Wear OS support.
* Show device list per group.
* Bookmark function.
* Ping ip addresses for faster input (optional).
* Ping device for status.
* Widget support.
* Dark mode support.
* Adaptive icon support.

Currently supported languages: english, dutch.

More features to be added in the upcoming releases.
